Palʊla Rembrandt kɛ Leyidi [[Peyibaa|Peeyiba]] ɛjaɖɛ taa kɛ [[hasɩyaɖɛ fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 15 wiye pɩnaɣ 1606 yaa 1607 taa nɛ ɛsɩ [[aloma fenaɣ]] kɩyakʊ 4 pɩnaɣ 1669  kɛ [[Amstɛrɩdam]] tɛtʊ taa, ɛɛwɛna pɩnzɩ 63. Palʊla-ɩ lɛ payayaɣ-ɩ se Rembrant Harmenszoon van Rijn. Rembrandt kɛ tɔlɩm tayʊ, saɣyʊ nɛ kɩlɛmɩŋ yaa anjaʊnaa lɩzɩyʊ. Ɛ-wɩlɩya sɔsaa taa nabayɩ kɔyɔ: Jacob van Swanenburgh, Pieter Lastman, Jan Lievens piyele e-sukuli pɩya lɛɛsɩ kɔyɔ: Ferdinand Bol, Gérard Dou, Willem Drost, Govaert Flinck, Carel Fabritius, Samuel van Hoogstraten, Nicolas Maes, Eeckhout. 

Leyidi nɛ Amstɛrɩdam tɛtʊ taa kɛ ɛkɩlɩ labʊʊ tʊmɩyɛ. Payaɣ ɛ-caa se Harmen Gerritszoon van Rijn nɛ e-ɖoo kɔyɔ Neeltje Willemsdr Zuytbrouck. Rembrandt halʊ kɛ payaɣ se Saskia van Uylenburgh nɛ pɛwɛna pɩɣa kʊɖʊmaɣ nɛ ŋga yɔ Cornelia van Rijn. Rembrandt kɛna weyi ɛwɛ tɔlɩm taya taa sɔsɔ nɔɔyʊ kɛ ɛtɛ alɩwaatʊ taa pɩkɩlɩna tɔlɩm taʊ mbʊ pɩɖɩɩzʊʊ ɛyaa yem yɔ. Ɛnʊ kɛŋna ɖɔɖɔ Holandɩ sukuli taa tɔlɩm tayaa taa sɔsɔ nɔɔyʊ kɛ pɩnzɩ mɩnɩŋ XVII taa.


